            </ol>
            <p>If the Client consents to the Supplier's use of Cookies on the Supplier's website and later wishes to withdraw that consent, the Client may manage and control the Supplier's privacy controls via the Client's web browser, including removing Cookies by deleting them from the browser history when exiting the site.</p>
